'Head, shoulders, beans, and paws, beans and paws. Tail, whiskers, beans, and paws, beans and paws. And triangle ears and beans of toes. Head, shoulders, beans, and paws, beans and paws.'

Oh, look at this bountiful harvest we have this year. The beans have grown strong and beautiful, a true blissful sight. All them fluffy feline workers kneaded the ground like they work in the biscuits factory, and put their paws to work. And, behold, the fruits of their work are here for all of us, feline fanatic fans, to enjoy. The beans grew nicely and are all ready to be harvested.

But there are also meowgical beans in this feline field. These beans aren't just beans, they grow bean memes, and sometimes even paw memes, going all the way to the cats' ankles. We harvested these special and magical bunch of beans and paws in meme form and brought them here - so we can all enjoy them all the way from the head, through the shoulders, to the beans and paws.
